name: Apple MacBook Pro 13-inch
description: The Apple MacBook Pro 13-inch comes with an Apple M1 chip, 8GB RAM, and 256GB SSD storage. A sleek and powerful laptop for professionals.

name: Samsung Galaxy S21
description: The Samsung Galaxy S21 features a 6.2-inch display, 8GB of RAM, and 128GB of storage. Powered by the Exynos 2100 processor.

name: Sony WH-1000XM4
description: The Sony WH-1000XM4 are over-ear wireless noise-canceling headphones with up to 30 hours of battery life and excellent sound quality.

name: Apple iPhone 13 Pro
description: The Apple iPhone 13 Pro features a 6.1-inch display, A15 Bionic chip, 128GB storage, and ProMotion for smooth scrolling and responsiveness.

name: Dell XPS 13
description: The Dell XPS 13 is a compact laptop featuring Intel's 11th generation Core i7 processor, 16GB of RAM, and a stunning 13-inch InfinityEdge display.

name: Bose QuietComfort 35 II
description: The Bose QuietComfort 35 II headphones offer exceptional sound quality and industry-leading noise cancellation for an immersive listening experience.

name: Microsoft Surface Pro 7
description: The Microsoft Surface Pro 7 is a 2-in-1 laptop with a 12.3-inch PixelSense display, Intel Core i5 processor, and 8GB RAM. Perfect for work and play.

name: LG 27UK850-W 27-Inch 4K UHD Monitor
description: The LG 27UK850-W 27-inch monitor features 4K UHD resolution, USB-C connectivity, and an IPS display for vivid colors and sharp details.

name: Samsung 1TB SSD 990 PRO
description: The Samsung 990 PRO 1TB SSD offers high-speed performance with NVMe technology, perfect for fast boot-up times and large file transfers.

name: GoPro HERO10 Black
description: The GoPro HERO10 Black is a waterproof action camera that shoots 5.3K video at 60fps and 23MP photos with HyperSmooth stabilization.
